Dog Task Manager (MongoDB + Mongoose Edition)

A fullstack web application for managing dog-related tasks for multiple accounts. Built with Express.js, Mongoose, and Next.js.

📁 Backend (Express + Mongoose)

📄 Features

REST API using Express.js

MongoDB data models via Mongoose

User, Dog, and Task models with relations

Task completion toggling

